Title: Fix redaction of remote site secrets in log messages
Class: security
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1741768335
Edition: cre
Level: 1
Version: 2.2.0p41

If the log level for <em>Web</em> is set to debug and the site has remote sites, the secrets used to
authenticate against the remote sites were logged to <code>var/log/web.log</code>.

This issue was found during internal review.

<em>Affected Versions</em>:

LI: 2.3.0
LI: 2.2.0
LI: 2.1.0 (EOL)

<em>Mitigations</em>:

Change the log level to verbose or less.

<em>Indicators of Compromise</em>:

Check <code>var/log/web.log for messages beginning with</code>Site states: `

<em>Vulnerability Management</em>:

We have rated the issue with a CVSS Score of 7.1 High
(<code>CVSS:4.0/AV:L/AC:L/AT:P/PR:L/UI:N/VC:H/VI:N/VA:N/SC:H/SI:H/SA:H</code>) and assigned <code>CVE-2025-2092</code>.
